        ],
        "text": ": سمعت أبا عبد الله جعفر بن محمد عليهما السلام يقول: احذروا سطوات الله  بالليل والنهار، فقلت: وما سطوات الله؟ فقال: أخذه على المعاصي ."
      },
      "translations": {
        "en.mulla-asgharali-m-m-jaffer": {
          "segments": [
            "8. And with the preceding chains of narration from ‘Ali ibn Mahzyar, from al-Nadhr, from Ibrahim ibn Abdul Hamid, from Zaid ibn al-Shahham who said: I heard Abu Abdillah Ja’far ibn Muhammad, peace be upon him, say: \"Beware of the dominant power of Allah, during the night and during the day.\" I asked: \"What is that dominant power?\" He said: \"When He seizes you for the sins.\""
          ],
          "text": "8. And with the preceding chains of narration from ‘Ali ibn Mahzyar, from al-Nadhr, from Ibrahim ibn Abdul Hamid, from Zaid ibn al-Shahham who said: I heard Abu Abdillah Ja’far ibn Muhammad, peace be upon him, say: \"Beware of the dominant power of Allah, during the night and during the day.\" I asked: \"What is that dominant power?\" He said: \"When He seizes you for the sins.\""
        }
